🏥 Hospital Management System (Django)

⚪ Overview

The Hospital Management System is a web-based application built using Django that helps manage 
hospital operations efficiently. It provides features for managing patients, doctors, appointments,
and medical records in a structured and user-friendly way.

Backend: Django (Python)
Frontend: HTML, CSS, Bootstrap
Other Tools: Crispy Forms


