step-9
MVT Design pattern (python followed this pattern )
model.view.templete
-------------------------------------------------
url mapping 
-----------
1-- Create a urls.py file in home app
2-- djangoproject------------url.py--------
    path(".include"("home.urls")),

//this home page will come first while run 


---------------------------------------------------
App URLS first empty path url define 
____________________________________
from django.urls import path.include
from .import views

urlpatterns = [
    path(",views.home, name = 'home'),


]


--------------------------------------------------
--define first view.in views.py
-home function

from django.http import HttpResponse

def home(request):
    return HttpResponse("HOME page is working")

def about(request):
    return HttpResponse("About page is working") 



then go to view.py and create functions like index,about,etc..

from django.shortcuts import render
from django.http import HttpResponse

def home(request):
    return render(request, 'home.html')

def about(request):
    return render(request, 'about.html')   


